# MindWell — Project Memory

## App Identity
- App renamed: "Reading Tracker" → "BookClub" → **MindWell**
- PWA manifest, layout metadata, header all updated

## Tech Stack
- Next.js App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4
- Supabase for data (books, sessions, priority_items, book_notes, quotes, connections)
- @dnd-kit for drag-and-drop (book reorder, calendar drag)
- next/font/google: Geist (body, --font-geist) + Lora (serif headings, --font-lora)

## Design System — Deep Still Well Aesthetic
Defined in `app/globals.css` via `@theme`:

**Well scale** (deep dark backgrounds + light text):
- well-50 #eef2ff — primary text on dark backgrounds
- well-100 #d4e2ff — secondary text
- well-200 #a8c4ff — muted text
- well-300 #6aa0f0
- well-400 #3a78d8
- well-500 #1e58b8
- well-600 #113e96
- well-700 #0a2870 — separator dots
- well-800 #1a2e4a — borders
- well-900 #0c1830 — card backgrounds
- well-950 #060e20 — page background

**Ripple scale** (glowing blue accent):
- ripple-400 #3aa8ff — soft accent/hover text
- ripple-500 #1090ff — hover state
- ripple-600 #0874e0 — primary buttons
- ripple-700 #0660c0
- ripple-800 #0044a0
- ripple-900 #002880/30 — subtle tint backgrounds

**Color mapping** (old systems → MindWell):
- Page bg: bg-well-950
- Card bg: bg-well-900
- Borders: border-well-800
- Primary text: text-well-50 / text-well-100
- Muted text: text-well-400 / text-well-500
- Primary button: bg-ripple-600 hover:bg-ripple-500
- Amber (priority/warning): amber-500 on dark (no bg-amber-50 — use bg-amber-500/10)
- Shadows: shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(6,14,32,0.6)]

## Key UI Patterns

### Dark Header (all pages)
`bg-well-950/80 backdrop-blur border-b border-well-800`
- MindWell title: `font-serif text-well-100`
- Primary button: `bg-ripple-600 hover:bg-ripple-500`

### Tabs (Notes page — 4 tabs: Outline, Scratch, Insights, Quotes)
Tab bar: `bg-well-950 border-b border-well-800`
- Active tab: `text-ripple-400 border-b-2 border-ripple-600`
- Inactive: `text-well-400 hover:text-well-200`

### Book Role Badges
- Primary (sort_order=1): violet — `text-violet-300 bg-violet-900/25 border-violet-800/40`
- Secondary (sort_order=2): amber — `text-amber-300 bg-amber-900/25 border-amber-800/40`

### Modal Style
`bg-well-900 border border-well-800 shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(6,14,32,0.6)]`

### Form Inputs
`border-well-800 bg-well-950 text-well-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ripple-600/20 focus:border-ripple-600/40`

### Quote Widgets (Quotes.tsx)
- Collapsed: preview text + page number + tags chips
- Expanded: full text + copy button (clipboard → checkmark 2s) + inline tag editor
- Tags: hash-based color from 8 dark palettes for consistency
- Auto-sorted by page_number ASC NULLS LAST

### Global Search
- Cmd+K shortcut toggles GlobalSearch overlay
- Debounced 300ms, grouped results by book
- Navigates to /books/[id]?tab=quotes|insights|outline|scratch

## File Structure
- `app/globals.css` — @theme: well + ripple color scales
- `app/layout.tsx` — Geist + Lora fonts, MindWell metadata
- `app/page.tsx` — Dashboard + GlobalSearch + Cmd+K handler
- `app/books/[id]/page.tsx` — Notes page: Outline/Scratch/Insights/Quotes tabs, ?tab= URL param
- `app/api/search/route.ts` — Search API (quotes + book_notes)
- `app/api/connections/route.ts` — GET/POST connections
- `app/api/connections/[id]/route.ts` — DELETE connection
- `components/Modal.tsx` — Dark modal wrapper
- `components/WeeklyCalendar.tsx` — Calendar grid (dark theme)
- `components/Quotes.tsx` — New quotes component (replaces QuotesWithHeadings.tsx)
- `components/GlobalSearch.tsx` — Full-screen search overlay
- `components/OutlineEditor.tsx` — Outline textarea

## Required DB Migrations
```sql
-- Tags on quotes
ALTER TABLE quotes ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS tags text[] DEFAULT '{}';

-- Connections table
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS connections (
  id uuid PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
  source_type text NOT NULL CHECK (source_type IN ('quote','note')),
  source_id uuid NOT NULL,
  target_type text NOT NULL CHECK (target_type IN ('quote','note')),
  target_id uuid NOT NULL,
  note text,
  created_at timestamptz DEFAULT now()
);

